# API Endpoint Structure

## Video Endpoints
- `POST /api/video/convert` - Format conversion
- `POST /api/video/edit` - Cut/trim/merge operations  
- `POST /api/video/effects` - Apply filters/effects
- `POST /api/video/extract-frames` - Extract frames as images

## Audio Endpoints
- `POST /api/audio/convert` - Audio format conversion
- `POST /api/audio/extract` - Extract audio from video
- `POST /api/audio/edit` - Cut/trim/fade operations
- `POST /api/audio/mix` - Mix multiple audio tracks

## Image Endpoints  
- `POST /api/image/convert` - Image format conversion
- `POST /api/image/edit` - Resize/crop/rotate operations
- `POST /api/image/batch` - Process multiple images

## Shared Endpoints
- `GET /api/download/:filename` - Download processed files
- `GET /api/metadata/:filename` - Get file information
- `POST /api/batch/process` - Batch operations
